Examples:

(Mr|Mrs|Dr)\. [A-Z][a-z]+ â†’ â€œMr. Johnâ€, â€œMrs. Smithâ€

(\\d{2})/(\\d{2})/(\\d{4}) â†’ captures day, month, year

5ï¸âƒ£ Lookarounds (Zero-width Assertions)

(?=...) â†’ Positive lookahead (must be followed by â€¦)

(?!...) â†’ Negative lookahead (must not be followed by â€¦)

(?<=...) â†’ Positive lookbehind (must be preceded by â€¦)

(?<!...) â†’ Negative lookbehind (must not be preceded by â€¦)

Examples:

