âš ï¸ Java regex: Lookbehind must be fixed length.

6ï¸âƒ£ Escaping Special Characters

Special chars: . ^ $ * + ? ( ) [ ] { } | \
To match literally â†’ escape with \\.
Example: "\\." matches a literal dot.

7ï¸âƒ£ Flags / Modes

Pattern.CASE_INSENSITIVE â†’ ignore case

Pattern.MULTILINE â†’ ^ and $ apply per line

Pattern.DOTALL â†’ . matches newline too

Inline flags:

